      "translation": "(1') To ..., Me-namnina , spouse of Gani , dedicated this ( bowl ) for ... of ..., the powerful man , king of Urim ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001903.7",
      "line_range": "7",
      "translation": "(6') The name of this bowl is \" My lady indeed cared for me !\"."
    }
